               Maseyk, Kadmiel and Seibt, Ulli and Commane, Roisin and Wehr,
               Richard and Krol, Maarten",
  abstract  = "Abstract. The uptake of carbonyl sulfide (COS) by terrestrial
               plants is linked to photosynthetic uptake of CO2 by a shared
               diffusion pathway. Applying COS as a photosynthesis tracer in
